lead_paragraph: Ireland produced a heroic performance to beat New Zealand 40-29 in Chicago on Saturday, ending the All Blacks' record 18-match winning streak and recording their first victory over the world champions in 29 tests spanning 111 years.

headline.print_headline: Inspired Ireland Beat All Blacks at Last to End Record Run
